quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  2,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  2,1,Alif Laaam Meeem
  2,2,yeh kitaab ( quran Majeed ) is mein kuch shak nahi ( ke klamِ khuda hai. khuda se ) darny walon ki rehnuma hai
  2,3,jo ghaib par imaan laatay aur aadaab ke sath namaz parhte aur jo kuch hum ne un ko ataa farmaya hai is mein se kharch karte hain
  2,4,aur jo kitaab ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tum par nazil hui aur jo kitaaben tum se pehlay ( payghambaroon par ) nazil huien sab par imaan laatay aur akhirat ka yaqeen rakhtay hain
  2,5,yahi log apne perwar-digaar ( ki taraf ) se hadaayat par hain aur yahi nijaat panay walay hain
  2,6,jo log kafir hain inhen tum nasiyaat karo ya nah karo un ke liye barabar hai. woh imaan nahi laane ke
  2,7,khuda ne un ke dilon aur kaanon par mohar laga rakhi hai aur un ki aankhon par parda ( para howa ) hai aur un ke liye bara azaab ( tayyar ) hai
  2,8,aur baaz log aisay hain jo kehte hain ke hum khuda par aur rozِ akhirat par imaan rakhtay hain halaank woh imaan nahi rakhtay
  2,9,yeh ( apne Pindar mein ) khuda ko aur mominoun ko chakma dete hain magar ( haqeeqat mein ) apne siwa kisi ko chakma nahi dete aur is se be khabar hain
  2,10,un ke dilon mein ( kufar ka ) marz tha. khuda ne un ka marz aur ziyada kar diya aur un ke jhoot bolnay ke sabab un ko dukh dainay wala azaab hoga
  2,11,"aur jab un se kaha jata hai ke zameen mein fasaad nah daalo to kehte hain, hum to islaah karne walay hain"
  2,12,"dekho yeh bilashuba mufsid hain, lekin khabar nahi rakhtay"
  2,13,"aur jab un se kaha jata hai ke jis terhan aur log imaan le aeye, tum bhi imaan le aao to kehte hain, bhala jis terhan be waqoof imaan le aeye hain isi terhan hum bhi imaan le ayen? sun lau ke yahi be waqoof hain lekin nahi jantay"
  2,14,"aur yeh log jab mominoun se mlitay hain to kehte hain ke hum imaan le aeye hain, aur jab apne shaitano mein jatay hain to ( un se ) kehte hain ke hum tumhare sath hain aur ( perwan Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam se ) to hum hansikiya karte hain"
  2,15,un ( mnafqon ) se khuda hansi karta hai aur inhen mohlat diye jata hai ke shararat wa sarkashi mein parre behak rahay hain
  2,16,"yeh woh log hain jinhon ne hadaayat chore kar gumraahi khareedi, to nah to un ki tijarat hi ne kuch naffa diya aur nah woh hadaayat yab hi hue"
  2,17,un ki misaal is shakhs ki si hai ke jis ne ( shab_e_ tareek mein ) aag jalayi. jab aag ne is ke ird gird ki cheeze roshan kee to khuda ne un ki roshni zael kar di aur un ko andheron mein chore diya ke kuch nahi dekhte
  2,18,"( yeh ) behray hain, gungay hain, andhay hain ke ( kisi terhan seedhay raste ki taraf ) lout hi nahi satke"
  2,19,ya un ki misaal meen ki si hai ke aasman se ( baras raha ho aur ) is mein andheray par andhera ( chhaa raha ) ho aur ( baadal ) garaj ( raha ) ho aur bijli ( kond rahi ) ho to yeh kadak se ( dar kar ) mout ke khauf se kaanon mein ungelian day len aur allah kafiroon ko ( har taraf se ) ghairay hue hai
  2,20,qareeb hai ke bijli ( ki chamak ) un ki aankhon ( ki Basarat ) ko uchak le jaye. jab bijli ( chamakti aur ) un par roshni daali hai to is mein chal parte hain aur jab andhera ho jata hai to kharray ke kharray reh jatay hain aur agar allah chahta to un ke kaanon ( ki shanwai ) aur aankhon ( ki benaye dono ) ko zael kar deta hai. be shak allah har cheez par Qadir hai
  2,21,logo! apne perwar-digaar ki abat karo jis ne tum ko aur tum se pehlay logon ko pedakiya taakay tum ( is ke azaab se ) bachcho
  2,22,jis ne tumhare liye zameen ko bichona aur aasman ko chhat banaya aur aasman se meen barsa kar tumahray khanay ke liye anwaa o aqsam ke meway peda kiye. pas kisi ko khuda ka humsar nah banaao. aur tum jantay to ho
  2,23,"aur agar tum ko is ( kitaab ) mein, jo hum ne apne bande ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam arabi ) par nazil farmai hai kuch shak ho to isi terhan ki aik sourat tum bhi bana lao aur khuda ke siwa jo tumahray madadgaar hon un ko bhi bulalo agar tum sachey ho"
  2,24,lekin agar ( aisa ) nah kar sakuu aur hargiz nahi kar sakuu ge to is aag se daro jis ka eendhan aadmi aur pathar hon ge ( aur jo ) kafiroon ke liye tayyar ki gayi hai
  2,25,"aur jo log imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay, un ko khushkhabri suna do ke un ke liye ( Nemat ke ) baagh hain, jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain. jab inhen un mein se kisi qisam ka mewa khanay ko diya jaye ga to kahin ge, yeh to wohi hai jo hum ko pehlay diya gaya tha. aur un ko aik dosray ke hum shakal meway diye jayen ge aur wahan un ke liye pak biwiyan hon gi aur woh bahishtoon mein hamesha rahen ge"
  2,26,"allah is baat se aar nahi karta ke machar ya is se barh kar kisi cheez ( maslan makhi makri waghera ) ki misaal bayan farmaiye. jo momin hain, woh yaqeen karte hain woh un ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se sach hai aur jo kafir hain woh kehte hain ke is misaal se khuda ki morad hikiya hai. is se ( khuda ) bahuton ko gumraah karta hai aur bahuton ko hadaayat bkhshta hai aur gumraah bhi karta to na farmanoon hi ko"
  2,27,jo khuda ke iqraar ko mazboot karne ke baad toar dete hain aur jis cheez ( yani rishtaqaraabat ) ke jore rakhnay ka allah ne hukum diya hai is ko qata kiye daaltay hain aur zameen mein kharabi karte hain yahi log nuqsaan uthany walay hain
  2,28,( kafroo! ) tum khuda se kyun kar munhkir ho satke ho jis haal mein ke tum be jaan they to is ne tum ko jaan bakhsh phir wohi tum ko maarta hai phir wohi tum ko zindah kere ga phir tum isi ki taraf lout kar jao ge
  2,29,wohi to hai jis ne sab cheeze jo zameen mein hain tumahray liye peda kee phir aasman ki taraf mutwajjah howa to un ko theek saat aasman bana diya aur woh har cheez se khabardaar hai
  2,30,aur ( woh waqt yaad karne ke qabil hai ) jab tumahray perwar-digaar ne firshton se farmaya ke mein zameen mein ( apna ) naib bananay wala hon. unhon ne kaha.kiya too is mein aisay shakhs ko naib banana chahta hai jo kharabian kere aur kasht wa khoon karta phiray aur hum teri tareef ke sath tasbeeh wa taqdees karte rehtay hain. ( khuda ne ) farmaya mein woh baatein jaanta hon jo tum nahi jantay
  2,31,aur is ne aadam ko sab ( cheezon ke ) naam sikhayiye phir un ko firshton ke samnaykiya aur farmaya ke agar tum sachey ho to mujhe un ke naam batao
  2,32,"unhon ne kaha, to pak hai. jitna ilm to ne hamein bakhsha hai, is ke siwa hamein kuch maloom nahi. be shak to Dana ( aur ) hikmat wala hai"
  2,33,( tab ) khuda ne ( aadam ko ) hukum diya ke aadam! tum un ko un ( cheezon ) ke naam batao. jab unhon ne un ko un ke naam betaye to ( firshton se ) farmaya kyun mein ne tum se nahi kaha tha ke mein asmano aur zameen ki ( sab ) posheeda baatein janta hon aur jo tum zahir karte ho aur jo posheeda karte ho ( sab ) mujh ko maloom hai
  2,34,aur jab hum ne firshton ko hukum diya ke aadam ke agay sajda karo to woh sjday mein gir parre magar shetan ne inkaarkiya aur ghuroor mein aakar kafir ban gaya
  2,35,aur hum ne kaha ke ae aadam tum aur tumhari biwi bahisht mein raho aur jahan se chaho be rok toak khao ( piyo ) lekin is darakht ke paas nah jana nahi to zaalmon mein ( daakhil ) ho jao ge
  2,36,"phir shetan ne dono ko wahan se phsla diya aur jis ( aish wa nishaat ) mein they, is se un ko nikalwa diya. tab hum ne hukum diya ke ( bahisht bareen se ) chalay jao. tum aik dosray ke dushman ho, aur tumahray liye zameen mein aik waqt taq thikana aur muaash ( muqarrar kar diya gaya ) hai"
  2,37,phir aadam ne apne perwar-digaar se kuch kalmaat sekhe ( aur maffi mangi ) to is ne un ka qasoor maaf kar diya be shak woh maaf karne wala ( aur ) sahib reham hai
  2,38,hum ne farmaya ke tum sab yahan se utar jao jab tumahray paas meri taraf se hadaayat puhanche to ( is ki pairwi karna ke ) jinhon ne meri hadaayat ki pairwi ki un ko nah kuch khauf hoga aur nah woh ghumnaak hon ge
  2,39,"aur jinhon ne ( is ko ) qubool nahkiya aur hamari aayton ko jhtlaya, woh dozakh mein jaane walay hain ( aur ) woh hamesha is mein rahen ge"
  2,40,ae Yaqoob ki aulaad! mere woh ahsaan yaad karo jo mein ne tum par kiye they aur is iqraar ko poora karo jo tum ne mujh sekiya tha. mein is iqraar ko poora karoon ga jo mein ne tum sekiya tha aur mujhi se drtay raho
  2,41,"aur jo kitaab mein ne ( apne rasool Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam par ) nazil ki hai jo tumhari kitaab torat ko sacha kehti hai, is par imaan lao aur is se munhkar awwal nah bano, aur meri aayton mein ( tahreef kar ke ) un ke badlay thori si qeemat ( yani dunyawi manafat ) nah haasil karo, aur mujhi se khauf rakho"
  2,42,"aur haq ko baatil ke sath nah mlao, aur sachhi baat ko jaan boojh kar nah chupao"
  2,43,aur namaz parha karo aur zakaat diya karo aur ( khuda ke agay ) jhuknay walon ke sath jhuka karo
  2,44,"( yeh )kiya ( aqal ki baat hai ke ) tum logon ko neki karne ko kehte ho aur apne tain faramosh kiye dete ho, halaank tum kitaab ( khuda ) bhi parhte ho.kiya tum samajte nahi ?"
  2,45,"aur ( ranj wa takleef mein ) sabr aur namaz se madad liya karo aur be shak namaz giran hai, magar un logon par ( giran nahi ) jo ijaz karne walay hain"
  2,46,aur jo yaqeen kiye hue hain ke woh apne perwar-digaar se milnay walay hain aur is ki taraf lout kar jaane walay hain
  2,47,"ae Yaqoob ki aulaad! mere woh ahsaan yaad karo, jo mein ne tum par kiye they aur yeh ke mein ne tum ko Jahan ke logon par fazeelat bakhsh thi"
  2,48,aur is din se daro jab koi kisi ke kuch kaam nah aeye aur nah kisi ki sifarish Manzoor ki jaye aur nah kisi se kisi terhan ka badla quboolkiya jaye aur nah log ( kisi aur terhan ) madad haasil kar saken
  2,49,aur ( hamaray un ahsanat ko yaad karo ) jab hum ne tum ko qomِ firaon se nijaat bakhsh woh ( log ) tum ko bara dukh dete they tumahray biton ko to qatal kar daaltay they aur baityon ko zindah rehne dete they aur is mein tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se barri ( sakht ) azmaish thi
  2,50,aur jab hum ne tumahray liye darya ko phaar diya tum ko nijaat di aur firaon ki qoum ko ghark kar diya aur tum dekh hi to rahay they
  2,51,aur jab hum ne moose se chalees raat ka wadakiya to tum ne un ke peechay bichhre ko ( mabood ) muqarrar kar liya aur tum zulm kar rahay they
  2,52,"phir is ke baad hum ne tum ko maaf kar diya, taakay tum shukar karo"
  2,53,"aur jab hum ne moose ko kitaab aur moajezae inayat kiye, taakay tum hadaayat haasil karo"
  2,54,"aur jab moose ne apni qoum ke logon se kaha ke bhayyo, tum ne bichhre ko ( mabood ) thehranay mein ( bara ) zulmkiya hai, to apne peda karne walay ke agay tauba karo aur apne tain halaak kar daalo. tumahray khaaliq ke nazdeek tumahray haq mein yahi behtar hai. phir is ne tumhara qasoor maaf kar diya. woh be shak maaf karne wala ( aur ) sahib reham hai"
  2,55,"aur jab tum ne ( moose ) se kaha ke moose, jab taq hum khuda ko samnay nah dekh len ge, tum par imaan nahi layein ge, to tum ko bijli ne aa ghaira aur tum dekh rahay they"
  2,56,"phir mout aa jaane ke baad hum ne tum ko azsrِ no zindah kar diya, taakay ahsaan manu"
  2,57,"aur baadal ka tum par saya kiye rakha aur ( tumahray liye ) mann o salwa utaartay rahay ke jo pakeeza cheeze hum ne tum ko ataa farmai hain, un ko khao ( piyo ) magar tumahray buzurgon ne un nematon ki kuch qader nah jani ( aur ) woh hamara kuch nahi bgarhte they balkay apna hi nuqsaan karte they"
  2,58,"aur jab hum ne ( un se ) kaha ke is gaon mein daakhil ho jao aur is mein jahan se chaho, khoob khao ( piyo ) aur ( dekhna ) darwazay mein daakhil hona to sajda karna aur hittah kehna, hum tumahray gunah maaf kar den ge aur neki karne walon ko aur ziyada den ge"
  2,59,"to jo zalim they, unhon ne is lafz ko, jis ka un ko hukum diya tha, badal kar is ki jagah aur lafz kehna shurukiya, pas hum ne ( un ) zaalmon par aasman se azaab nazilkiya, kyunkay nafarmaniyan kiye jatay they"
  2,60,"aur jab moose ne apni qoum ke liye ( khuda se ) pani manga to hum ne kaha ke apni laathi pathar par maro. ( unhon ne laathi maari ) to phir is mein se baara chashmay phoot niklay, aur tamam logon ne apna apna ghaat maloom kar ( ke pani pi ) liya. ( hum ne hukum diya ke ) khuda ki ( ataa farmai hui ) rozi khao aur piyo, magar zameen mein fasaad nah karte phirna"
  2,61,"aur jab tum ne kaha ke moose! hum se aik ( hi ) khanay par sabr nahi ho sakta to apne perwar-digaar se dua kijiyej ke tarkari aur kakri aur gheehon aur msor aur pyaaz ( waghera ) jo nabataat zameen se ugti hain, hamaray liye peda kar day. unhon ne kaha ke bhala umdah cheeze chore kar un ke aiwz naaqis cheeze kyun chahtay hon. ( agar yahi cheeze matloob hain ) to kisi shehar mein ja uttro, wahan jo mangte ho, mil jaye ga. aur ( aakhir kaar ) zillat ( wa ruswai ) aur mohtaji ( wabay nawai ) un se chimta di gayi aur woh allah ke ghazab mein girftar ho gay. yeh is liye ke woh allah ki aayton se inkaar karte they aur ( is ke ) nabiyo ko na-haq qatal kar dete they. ( yani ) yeh is liye ke nafarmani kiye jatay aur hadd se barhay jatay they"
  2,62,"jo log musalman hain ya yahodi ya isaai ya sitara parast, ( yani koi shakhs kisi qoum o mazhab ka ho ) jo khuda aur roz qayamat par imaan laaye ga, aur naik amal kere ga, to aisay logon ko un ( ke aamaal ) ka sila khuda ke haan miley ga aur ( qayamat ke din ) un ko nah kisi terhan ka khauf hoga aur nah woh gham naak hon ge"
  2,63,"aur jab hum ne tum se ehad ( kar ) liya aur koh-e tor ko tum par utha kharakiya ( aur hukum diya ) ke jo kitaab hum ne tum ko di hai, is ko zor se pakdae raho, aur jo is mein ( likha ) hai, usay yaad rakho, taakay ( azaab se ) mehfooz raho"
  2,64,to tum is ke baad ( ehad se ) phir gay aur agar tum par khuda ka fazl aur is ki meharbani nah hoti to tum khasaray mein parre gay hotay
  2,65,"aur tum un logon ko khoob jantay hon, jo tum mein se haftay ke din ( machhli ka shikaar karne ) mein hadd se tajawaz kar gay they, to hum ne un se kaha ke zaleel vkhwar bandar ho jao"
  2,66,aur is qissay ko is waqt ke logon ke liye aur jo un ke baad anay walay they Ibrat aur parhaiz gaaron ke liye nasiyaat bana diya
  2,67,"aur jab moose ne apni qoum ke logon se kaha ke khuda tum ko hukum deta hai ke aik bail zibah karo. woh bolay,kiya tum hum se hansi karte ho. ( moose ne ) kaha ke mein allah ki panah mangta hon ke nadaan banon"
  2,68,"unhon ne kaha ke apne perwar-digaar se iltija kijiyej ke woh hamein yeh betaye ke woh bail kis terhan ka ho. ( moose ne ) kaha ke perwar-digaar farmata hai ke woh bail nah to boorha ho aur nah bitchrha, balkay un ke darmain ( yani jawan ) ho. jaissa tum ko hukum diya gaya hai, waisa karo"
  2,69,"unhon ne kaha ke perwar-digaar se darkhwast kijiyej ke hum ko yeh bhi betaye ke is ka rang kaisa ho. moose ne kaha, perwar-digaar farmata hai ke is ka rang gehra zard ho ke dekhnay walon ( ke dil ) ko khush kar deta ho"
  2,70,"unhon ne kaha ke ( ab ke ) perwar-digaar se phir darkhwast kijiyej ke hum ko bta day ke woh aur kis kis terhan ka ho, kyunkay bohat se bail hamein aik dosray ke mushaba maloom hotay hain, ( phir ) khuda ne chaha to hamein theek baat maloom ho jaye gi"
  2,71,"moose ne kaha ke khuda farmata hai ke woh bail kaam mein laga howa nah ho, nah to zameen jootna ho aur nah khaiti ko pani deta ho. is mein kisi terhan ka daagh nah ho. kehnay lagey, ab tum ne sab baatein durust bta den. gharz ( barri mushkil se ) unhon ne is bail ko zibahkiya, aur woh aisa karne walay they nahi"
  2,72,"aur jab tum ne 1 shakhs ko qatalkiya, to is mein baahum jhagrnay lagey. lekin jo baat tum chhupa rahay they, khuda is ko zahir karne wala tha"
  2,73,to hum ne kaha ke is bail ka koi sa tukda maqtool ko maro. is terhan khuda mardon ko zindah karta hai aur tum ko apni ( qudrat ki ) nishanain dekhata hai taakay tum samjhoo
  2,74,"phir is ke baad tumahray dil sakht ho gay. goya woh pathar hain ya un se bhi ziyada sakht. aur pathar to baze aisay hotay hain ke un mein se chashmay phoot nikaltay hain, aur baze aisay hotay hain ke phatt jatay hain, aur un mein se pani niklny lagta hai, aur baze aisay hotay hain ke khuda ke khauf se gir parte hain, aur khuda tumahray amlon se be khabar nahi"
  2,75,"( momino )kiya tum umeed rakhtay ho ke yeh log tumahray ( deen ke ) qaail ho jayen ge, ( halaank ) un mein se kuch log klamِ khuda ( yani torat ) ko suntay, phir is ke samajh lainay ke baad is ko jaan boojh kar badal dete rahay hain"
  2,76,"aur yeh log jab mominoun se mlitay hain to kehte hain, hum imaan le aeye hain. aur jab aapas mein aik dosray se mlitay hain to kehte hain, jo baat khuda ne tum par zahir farmai hai, woh tum un ko is liye betaye dete ho ke ( qayamat ke din ) isi ke hawalay se tumahray perwar-digaar ke samnay tum ko ilzaam den.kiya tum samajte nahi ?"
  2,77,"kiya yeh log yeh nahi jantay ke jo kuch yeh chupatay aur jo kuch zahir karte hain, khuda ko ( sab ) maloom hai"
  2,78,aur baaz un mein un parh hain ke apne baatil khayalat ke siwa ( khuda ki ) kitaab se waaqif hi nahi aur woh sirf zan se kaam letay hain
  2,79,"to un logon par afsos hai jo apne haath se to kitaab likhte hain aur kehte yeh hain ke yeh khuda ke paas se ( aayi ) hai, taakay is ke aiwz thori se qeemat ( yani dunewi Manfiat ) haasil karen. un par afsos hai, is liye ke ( be asal baatein ) apne haath se likhte hain aur ( phir ) un par afsos hai, is liye ke aisay kaam karte hain"
  2,80,"aur kehte hain ke ( dozakh ki ) aag hamein chand roz ke siwa chhoo hi nahi sakay gi. un se pucho,kiya tum ne khuda se iqraar le rakha hai ke khuda apne iqraar ke khilaaf nahi kere ga. ( nahi ), balkay tum khuda ke baray mein aisi baatein kehte ho jin ka tumhe mutlaq ilm nahi"
  2,81,"haan jo buray kaam kere, aur is ke gunah ( har taraf se ) ghair len to aisay log dozakh ( mein jaane ) walay hain ( aur ) woh hamesha is mein ( jaltay ) rahen ge"
  2,82,"aur jo imaan layein aur naik kaam karen, woh jannat ke maalik hon ge ( aur ) hamesha is mein ( aish karte ) rahen ge"
  2,83,"aur jab hum ne bani Israel se ehad liya ke khuda ke siwa kisi ki ibadat nah karna aur maa baap aur rishta daaron aur yatimon aur mohtajon ke sath bhalai karte rehna aur logon se achi baatein kehna, aur namaz parhte aur zakaat dete rehna, to chand shakhson ke siwa tum sab ( is ehad se ) munh phair kar phir baithy"
  2,84,"aur jab hum ne tum se ehad liya ke aapas mein kasht wa khoon nah karna aur apne ko un ke watan se nah nikalna to tum ne iqraar kar liya, aur tum ( is baat ke ) gawah ho"
  2,85,"phir tum wohi ho ke apnon ko qatal bhi kar dete ho aur apne mein se baaz logon par gunah aur zulm se charhai karkay inhen watan se nikaal bhi dete ho, aur agar woh tumahray paas qaid ho kar ayen to badla day kar un ko churra bhi letay ho, halaank un ka nikaal dena hi tum ko haraam tha. ( yeh )kiya ( baat hai ke ) tum ktabِ ( khuda ) ke baaz ehkaam ko to mantay ho aur baaz se inkaar kiye dete ho, to jo tum mein se aisi harkat karen, un ki saza is ke siwa aurkiya ho sakti hai ke duniya ki zindagi mein to ruswai ho aur qayamat ke din sakht se sakht azaab mein daal diye jayen aur jo kaam tum karte ho, khuda un se ghaafil nahi"
  2,86,yeh woh log hain jinhon ne akhirat ke badlay duniya ki zindagi khareedi. so nah to un se azaab hi halkakiya jaye ga aur nah un ko ( aur terhan ki ) madad miley gi
  2,87,"aur hum ne moose ko kitaab inayat ki aur un ke peechay yakke baad deegray paighambar bhaijtay rahay aur eesa ban maryam ko khulay nishanaat bakhshay aur rooh al quds ( yani jbryil ) se un ko madad di. to jab koi paighambar tumahray paas aisi baatein le kar aeye, jin ko tumhara jee nahi chahta tha, to tum sarkash ho jatay rahay, aur aik giroh ( anbia ) ko to jutlatay rahay aur aik giroh ko qatal karte rahay"
  2,87,( mslmano ) tum par ( khuda ke raste mein ) larna farz kardiya gaya hai woh tumhe nagawaar to hoga magar ajab nahi ke aik cheez tum ko buri lagey aur woh tumahray haq mein bhali ho aur ajab nahi ke aik cheez tum ko bhali lagey aur woh tumahray liye muzir ho. aur un baton ko ) khuda hi behtar jaanta hai aur tum nahi jantay
  2,88,"aur kehte hain, hamaray dil parday mein hain. ( nahi ) balkay allah ne un ke kufar ke sabab un par laanat kar rakhi hai. pas yeh thoray hi par imaan laatay hain"
  2,89,"aur jab allah ke haan se un ke paas kitaab aayi jo un ki ( aasmani ) kitaab ki bhi tasdeeq karti hai, aur woh pehlay ( hamesha ) kafiroon par fatah manga karte they, to jis cheez ko woh khoob pehchante they, jab un ke paas aap_hnchi to is se kafir ho gay. pas kafiroon par allah ki laanat"
  2,90,"jis cheez ke badlay unhon ne apne tain beech dala, woh bohat buri hai, yani is jalan se ke khuda apne bundon mein jis par chahta hai, apni meharbani se nazil farmata hai. khuda ki nazil ki hui kitaab se kufar karne lagey to woh ( is ke ) ghazab baalaye ghazab mein mubtala ho gay. aur kafiroon ke liye zaleel karne wala azaab hai"
  2,91,"aur jab un se kaha jata hai ke jo ( kitaab ) khuda ne ( ab ) nazil farmai hai, is ko manu. to kehte hain ke jo kitaab hum par ( pehlay ) nazil ho chuki hai, hum to isi ko mantay hain. ( yani ) yeh is ke siwa kisi aur ( kitaab ) ko nahi mantay, halaank woh ( sara sar ) sachhi hai aur jo un ki ( aasmani ) kitaab hai, is ki bhi tasdeeq karti hai. ( un se ) keh do ke agar tum sahib imaan hotay to allah ke payghambaroon ko pehlay hi kyun qatalkiya karte"
  2,92,aur moose tumahray paas khulay hue Muajzaat le kar aeye to tum un ke ( koh-e tor jaane ke ) baad bichhre ko mabood bana baithy aur tum ( apne hi haq mein ) zulm karte they
  2,93,"aur jab hum ne tum ( logon ) se ehad wasiq liya aur koh tor ko tum par utha kharakiya ( aur hukum diya ke ) jo ( kitaab ) hum ne tum ko di hai, is ko zor se pakro aur jo tumhe hukum hota hai ( is ko ) suno to woh ( jo tumahray barray they ) kehnay lagey ke hum ne sun to liya lekin mantay nahi. aur un ke kufar ke sabab bitchrha ( goya ) un ke dilon mein rich gaya tha. ( ae paighambar un se ) keh do ke agar tum momin ho to tumhara imaan tum ko buri baat batata hai"
  2,94,keh do ke agar akhirat ka ghar aur logon ( yani musalmanoon ) ke liye nahi aur khuda ke nazdeek tumahray hi liye makhsoos hai to agar sachey ho to mout ki arzoo to karo
  2,95,"lekin un aamaal ki wajah se, jo un ke haath agay bhaij chuke hain, yeh kabhi is ki arzoo nahi karen ge, aur khuda zaalmon se ( khoob ) waaqif hai"
  2,96,"balkay un ko tum aur logon se zindagi ke kahin harees dekho ge, yahan taq ke mushrikon se bhi. un mein se har aik yahi khwahish karta hai ke kash woh hazaar baras jeeta rahay, magar itni lambi Umar is ko mil bhi jaye to usay azaab se to nahi churra sakti. aur jo kaam yeh karte hain, khuda un ko dekh raha hai"
  2,97,"keh do ke jo shakhs jbryil ka dushman ho ( is ko ghusse mein mar jana chahiye ) is ne to ( yeh kitaab ) khuda ke hukum se tumahray dil par nazil ki hai jo pehli kitabon ki tasdeeq karti hai, aur imaan walon ke liye hadaayat aur basharat hai"
  2,98,jo shakhs khuda ka aur is ke firshton ka aur is ke payghambaroon ka aur jbryil aur mikaeel ka dushman ho to aisay kafiroon ka khuda dushman hai
  2,99,"aur hum ne tumahray paas suljhi hui ayatain arsaal farmai hain, aur un se inkaar wohi karte hain jo badkaar hain"
  2,100,un logon ne jab ( khuda se ) ehad wasiqkiya to un mein se aik fareeq ne is ko ( kisi cheez ki terhan ) pheink diya. haqeeqat yeh hai ke un mein aksar be imaan hain
  2,101,"aur jab un ke paas allah ki taraf se paighambar ( aakhir uz zamaan ) aeye, aur woh un ki ( aasmani ) kitaab ki bhi tasdeeq karte hain to jin logon ko kitaab di gayi thi, un mein se aik jamaat ne khuda ki kitaab ko peeth peechay pheink diya, goya woh jantay hi nahi"
  2,102,"aur un ( hazliyaat ) ke peechay lag gay jo Sulaiman ke ahdِ saltanat mein shyatin parha karte they aur Sulaiman ne mutlaq kufar ki baat nahi ki, balkay shetan hi kufar karte they ke logon ko jaadoo sikhate they. aur un baton ke bhi ( peechay lag gay ) jo shehar babul mein do firshton ( yani ) harwat aur Maruat par utri theen. aur woh dono kisi ko kuch nahi sikhate they, jab taq yeh nah keh dete ke hum to (zaryaٴ ) azmaish hain. tum kufar mein nah parro. gharz log un se ( aisa ) jaadoo sikhte, jis se miyan biwi mein judai daal den. aur khuda ke hukum ke siwa woh is ( jaadoo ) se kisi ka kuch bhi nahi bigaar satke they. aur kuch aisay ( mantar ) sikhte jo un ko nuqsaan hi pohanchate aur faida kuch nah dete. aur woh jantay they ke jo shakhs aisi cheezon ( yani sehar aur mantar waghera ) ka khredar hoga, is ka akhirat mein kuch hissa nahi. aur jis cheez ke aiwz unhon ne apni jaanun ko beech dala, woh buri thi. kash woh ( is baat ko ) jantay"
  2,103,"aur agar woh imaan laatay aur parhaiz gari karte to khuda ke haan se bohat acha sila milta. ae kash, woh is se waaqif hotay"
  2,104,"ae ahal imaan! ( guftagu ke waqt pighmbrِ khuda se ) ra-ana nah kaha karo. anzarna kaha karo. aur khoob sun rakho, aur kafiroon ke liye dukh dainay wala azaab hai"
  2,105,"jo log kafir hain, ahal kitaab ya mushriq woh is baat ko pasand nahi karte ke tum par tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se kher ( wa barkat ) nazil ho. aur khuda to jis ko chahta hai, apni rehmat ke sath khaas kar laita hai aur khuda barray fazl ka maalik hai"
  2,106,hum jis aayat ko mansookh kar dete ya usay faramosh kara dete hain to is se behtar ya waisi hi aur aayat bhaij dete hain.kiya tum nahi jantay ke khuda har baat par Qadir hai
  2,107,"tumhe maloom nahi ke asmano aur zameen ki badshahat khuda hi ki hai, aur khuda ke siwa tumhara koi dost aur madad gaar nahi"
  2,108,"kiya tum yeh chahtay ho ke apne paighambar se isi terhan ke sawal karo, jis terhan ke sawal pehlay moose se kiye gay they. aur jis shakhs ne imaan ( chore kar is ) ke badlay kufar liya, woh seedhay raste se bhatak gaya"
  2,109,bohat se ahal kitaab apne dil ki jalan se yeh chahtay hain ke imaan laa chikane ke baad tum ko phir kafir bana den. halaank un par haq zahir ho chuka hai. to tum maaf kardo aur dar guzar karo. yahan taq ke khuda apna ( dosra ) hukum beje. be shak khuda har baat par Qadir hai
  2,110,"aur namaz ada karte raho aur zakaat dete raho. aur jo bhalai apne liye agay bhaij rakho ge, is ko khuda ke haan pa lau ge. kuch shak nahi ke khuda tumahray sab kamon ko dekh raha hai"
  2,111,aur ( yahodi aur isaai ) kehte hain ke yahudion aur esaion ke siwa koi bahisht mein nahi jaane ka. yeh un logon ke khayalat baatil hain. ( ae paighambar un se ) keh do ke agar sachey ho to Daleel paish karo
  2,112,"haan jo shakhs khuda ke agay gardan jhuka day, ( yani imaan le aeye ) aur woh naiko car bhi ho to is ka sila is ke perwar-digaar ke paas hai aur aisay logon ko ( qayamat ke din ) nah kisi terhan ka khauf hoga aur nah woh ghumnaak hon ge"
  2,113,aur yahodi kehte hain ke isaai raste par nahi aur isaai kehte hain ke yahodi raste par nahi. halaank woh kitaab ( Ellahi ) parhte hain. isi terhan bilkul unhi ki si baat woh log kehte hain jo ( kuch ) nahi jantay ( yani mushriq ) to jis baat mein yeh log ikhtilaaf kar rahay khuda qayamat ke din is ka un mein faisla kar day ga
  2,114,"aur is se barh kar zalim kon, jo khuda ki masjidoon mein khuda ke naam ka zikar kiye jaane ko mana kere aur un ki weerani mein Saee ho. un logon ko kuch haq nahi ke un mein daakhil hon, magar drtay hue. un ke liye duniya mein ruswai hai aur akhirat mein bara azaab"
  2,115,aur mashriq aur maghrib sab khuda hi ka hai. to jidhar tum rukh karo. idhar khuda ki zaat hai. be shak khuda sahib wusat aur bakhabar hai
  2,116,"aur yeh log is baat ke qaail hain ke khuda aulaad rakhta hai. ( nahi ) woh pak hai, balkay jo kuch asmano aur zameen mein hai, sab isi ka hai aur sab is ke farmaa bardaar hain"
  2,117,( wohi ) asmano aur zameen ka peda karne valahe. jab koi kaam karna chahta hai to is ko irshad farma deta hai ke hoja to woh ho jata hai .
  2,118,"aur jo log ( kuch ) nahi jantay ( yani mushriq ) woh kehte hain ke khuda hum se kalaam kyun nahi karta. ya hamaray paas koi nishani kyun nahi aati. isi terhan jo log un se pehlay they, woh bhi unhi ki si baateinkiya karte they. un logon ke dil aapas mein mlitay jaltay hain. jo log sahib yaqeen hain, un ke ( samjhane ke ) liye nishanain bayan kar di hain"
  2,119,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tum ko sachaai ke sath khushkhabri sunanay wala aur darane wala bana kar bheja hai. aur ahal dozakh ke baray mein tum se kuch prssh nahi hogi
  2,120,"aur tum se nah to yahodi kabhi khush hon ge aur nah isaai, yahan taq ke tum un ke mazhab ki pairwi ikhtiyar karlo. ( un se ) keh do ke khuda ki hadaayat ( yani deen islam ) hi hadaayat hai. aur ( ae paighambar ) agar tum apne paas ilm ( yani wahi khuda ) ke aa jaane par bhi un ki khawahishon par chalo ge to tum ko ( azaab ) khuda se ( bachanay wala ) nah koi dost hoga aur nah koi madadgaar"
  2,121,"jin logon ko hum ne kitaab inayat ki hai, woh is ko ( aisa ) parhte hain jaissa is ke parhnay ka haq hai. yahi log is par imaan rakhnay walay hain, aur jo is ko nahi mantay, woh khasara panay walay hain"
  2,122,"ae bani Israel ! mere woh ahsaan yaad karo, jo mein ne tum par kiye aur yeh ke mein ne tum ko ehley aalam par fazeelat bakhsh"
  2,123,"aur is din se daro jab koi shakhs kisi shakhs ke kuch kaam nah aeye, aur nah is se badla quboolkiya jaye aur nah is ko kisi ki sifarish kuch faida day aur nah logon ko ( kisi aur terhan ki ) madad mil sakay"
  2,124,aur jab perwar-digaar ne chand baton mein ibrahim ki azmaish ki to un mein poooray utre. khuda ne kaha ke mein tum ko logon ka peshwa bunun ga. unhon ne kaha ke ( perwar-digaar ) meri aulaad mein se bhi ( peshwa banaiyo ). khuda ne farmaya ke hamara iqraar zaalmon ke liye nahi howa karta
  2,125,"aur jab hum ne Khana kaaba ko logon ke liye jama honay aur aman panay ki jagah muqarrarkiya aur ( hukum diya ke ) jis maqam par ibrahim kharray hue they, is ko namaz ki jagah bana lau. aur ibrahim aur asmayl ko kaha ke tuwaf karne walon aur aitekaf karne walon aur ruku karne walon aur sajda karne walon ke liye mere ghar ko pak saaf rakha karo"
  2,126,"aur jab ibrahim ne dua ki ke ae perwar-digaar, is jagah ko aman ka shehar bana aur is ke rehne walon mein se jo khuda par aur rozِ akhirat par imaan layein, un ke khanay ko meway ataa kar, to khuda ne farmaya ke jo kafir hoga, mein is ko bhi kisi qader mtmta karoon ga, ( magar ) phir is ko ( azaab ) dozakh ke ( bhgtne ke ) liye nachar kardoon ga, aur woh buri jagah hai"
  2,127,"aur jab ibrahim aur asmayl beeet allah ki bunyadain onche kar rahay they ( to dua kiye jatay they ke ) ae perwar-digaar, hum se yeh khidmat qubool farma. be shak to suneney wala ( aur ) jan-nay wala hai"
  2,128,"ae perwar-digaar, hum ko apna farmanbardar banaye rakiyo. aur hamari aulaad mein se bhi aik giroh ko apna Mutee banaye rahev, aur ( perwar-digaar ) hamein tareeq ibadat bta aur hamaray haal par ( reham ke sath ) tavajja farma. be shak to tavajja frmane wala meharban hai"
  2,129,"ae perwar-digaar, un ( logon ) mein inhen mein se aik paighambar maboos kejio jo un ko teri ayatain parh parh kar sunaya kere aur kitaab aur danai sikhaya kere aur un ( ke dilon ) ko pak saafkiya kere. be shak to ghalib aur sahib hikmat hai"
  2,130,"aur ibrahim ke deen se kon ro gardani kar sakta hai, bajuz is ke jo nihayat nadaan ho. hum ne un ko duniya mein bhi munhtakhibkiya tha aur akhirat mein bhi woh ( zumrahٴ ) sulhaا mein se hon ge"
  2,131,jab un se un ke perwar-digaar ne farmaya ke islam le aao to unhon ne arz ki ke mein rab alaalmin ke agay sir itaat khham karta hon
  2,132,aur abrhim ne apne biton ko isi baat ki wasiyat ki aur Yaqoob ne bhi ( apne frzndon se yahi kaha ) ke beta khuda ne tumahray liye yahi deen pasand farmaya hai to marna hai to musalman hi marna
  2,133,"bhala jis waqt Yaqoob wafaat panay lagey to tum is waqt mojood they, jab unhon ne apne biton se poocha ke mere baad tum kis ki ibadat karo ge, to unhon ne kaha ke aap ke mabood aur aap ke baap dada ibrahim aur asmayl aur Ishaq ke mabood ki ibadat karen ge jo mabood yaktaa hai aur hum usi ke hukum bardaar hain"
  2,134,yeh jamaat guzar chuki. un ko unn ke aamaal ( ka badla miley ga ) aur tum ko tumhare aamaal ( ka ) aur jo amal woh karte they un ki prssh tum se nahi hogi
  2,135,"aur ( yahodi aur isaai ) kehte hain ke yahodi ya isaai ho jao to seedhay raste par lag jao. ( ae paighambar un se ) keh do, ( nahi ) balkay ( hum ) deen ibrahim ( ikhtiyar kiye hue hain ) jo aik khuda ke ho rahay they aur mushrikon mein se nah they"
  2,136,"( mslmano ) kaho ke hum khuda par imaan laaye aur jo ( kitaab ) hum par utri, is par aur jo ( saheefay ) ibrahim aur asmayl aur Ishaq aur Yaqoob aur un ki aulaad par nazil hue un par aur jo ( kitaaben ) moose aur eesa ko ataa huien, un par, aur jo aur payghambaroon ko un ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se milein, un par ( sab par imaan laaye ) hum un peghambaron mein se kisi mein kuch farq nahi karte aur hum isi ( khuday-e wahid ) ke farmanbardar hain"
  2,137,to agar yeh log bhi isi terhan imaan le ayen jis terhan tum imaan le aeye ho to hadaayat yab ho jayen aur agar munh phair len ( aur nah manen ) to woh ( tumhare ) mukhalif hain aur un ke muqablay mein tumhen khuda kaafi hai. aur woh suneney wala ( aur ) jan-nay wala hai
  2,138,( keh do ke hum ne ) khuda ka rang ( ikhtiyar kar liya hai ) aur khuda se behtar rang kis ka ho sakta hai. aur hum isi ki ibadat karne walay hain
  2,139,"( un se ) kaho,kiya tum khuda ke baray mein hum se jhagarte ho, halaank wohi hamara aur tumahra perwar-digaar hai aur hum ko hamaray aamaal ( ka badla miley ga ) aur tum ko tumhare aamaal ( ka ) aur hum khaas isi ki ibadat karne walay hain"
  2,140,"( ae yahood wa nasari )kiya tum is baat ke qaail ho ke ibrahim aur asmayl aur Ishaq aur Yaqoob aur un ki aulaad yahodi ya isaai they. ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam un se ) kaho ke bhala tum ziyada jantay ho ya khuda? aur is se barh kar zalim kon, jo khuda ki shahadat ko, jo is ke paas ( kitaab mein mojood ) hai chupaye. aur jo kuch tum kar rahay ho, khuda is se ghaafil nahi"
  2,141,"yeh jamaat guzar chuki. un ko woh ( miley ga ) jo unhon nekiya, aur tum ko woh jo tum nekiya. aur jo amal woh karte they, is ki prssh tum se nahi hogi"
  2,142,"ahmaq log kahin ge ke musalman jis qble par ( pehlay se chalay atay ) they ( ab ) is se kyun munh phair baithy. tum keh do ke mashriq aur maghrib sab khuda hi ka hai. woh jis ko chahta hai, seedhay raste par chalata hai"
  2,143,"aur isi terhan hum ne tum ko amtِ motadil banaya hai, taakay tum logon par gawah bano aur paighambar ( aakhir uz zamaan ) tum par gawah banin. aur jis qble par tum ( pehlay ) they, is ko hum ne is liye muqarrarkiya tha ke maloom karen, kon ( hamaray ) paighambar ka tabay rehta hai, aur kon ultay paon phir jata hai. aur yeh baat ( yani tehweel qibla logon ko ) giran maloom hui, magar jin ko khuda ne hadaayat bakhsh ( woh usay giran nahi samajte ) aur khuda aisa nahi ke tumahray imaan ko yuhin kho day. khuda to logon par bara meharban ( aur ) sahib rehmat hai"
  2,144,"( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum tumhara aasman ki taraf munh phair phair kar dekhna dekh rahay hain. so hum tum ko isi qble ki taraf jis ko tum pasand karte ho, munh karne ka hukum den ge to apna munh masjid haraam ( yani Khana kaaba ) ki taraf phair lau. aur tum log jahan howa karo, ( namaz parhnay ke waqt ) isi masjid ki taraf munh kar liya karo. aur jin logon ko kitaab di gayi hai, woh khoob jantay hain ke ( naya qibla ) un ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se haq hai. aur jo kaam yeh log karte hain, khuda un se be khabar nahi"
  2,145,"aur agar tum un ehley kitaab ke paas tamam nishanain bhi le kar aao, to bhi yeh tumahray qble ki pairwi nah karen. aur tum bhi un ke qble ki pairwi karne walay nahi ho. aur un mein se bhi baaz baaz ke qble ke pairo nahi. aur agar tum bawajood is ke ke tumahray paas Danish ( yani wahi khuda ) aa chuki hai, un ki khawahishon ke peechay chalo ge to zaalmon mein ( daakhil ) ho jao ge"
  2,146,"jin logon ko hum ne kitaab di hai, woh un ( paighambar aakhir uz zamaan ) ko is terhan pehchante hain, jis terhan apne biton ko pehchana karte hain, magar aik fareeq un mein se sachhi baat ko jaan boojh kar chhupa raha hai"
  2,147,"( ae paighambar, yeh naya qibla ) tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se haq hai to tum hargiz shak karne walon mein nah hona"
  2,148,aur har aik ( firqay ) ke liye aik simt ( muqarrar ) hai. jidhar woh ( ibadat ke waqt ) munhkiya karte hain. to tum nakiyon mein Sabqat haasil karo. tum jahan raho ge khuda tum sab ko jama karle ga. be shak khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
  2,149,"aur tum jahan se niklo, ( namaz mein ) apna munh masjid mohtaram ki taraf kar liya karo be shak woh tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se haq hai. aur tum log jo kuch karte ho. khuda is se be khabar nahi"
  2,150,"aur tum jahan se niklo, masjid-e mohtaram ki taraf munh ( karkay namaz parha ) karo. aur mslmano, tum jahan howa karo, isi ( masjid ) ki taraf rukhkiya karo. ( yeh takeed ) is liye ( ki gayi hai ) ke log tum ko kisi terhan ka ilzaam nah day saken. magar un mein se jo zalim hain, ( woh ilzaam den to den ) so un se mat darna aur mujhi se drtay rehna. aur yeh bhi maqsood hai ke tum ko apni tamam naematain bakhson aur yeh bhi ke tum raah e raast par chalo"
  2,151,"jis terhan ( mnjmlh aur nematon ke ) hum ne tum mein tumhen mein se aik rasool beje hain jo tum ko hamari ayatain parh parh kar sunaate aur tumhe pak banatay aur kitaab ( yani quran ) aur danai sikhate hain, aur aisi baatein batatay hain, jo tum pehlay nahi jantay they"
  2,152,so tum mujhe yaad karo. mein tumhe yaadkiya karoon ga. aur mere ahsaan mantay rehna aur nashkri nah karna
  2,153,ae imaan walo sabr aur namaz se madad liya karo be shak khuda sabr karne walon ke sath hai
  2,154,aur jo log khuda ki raah mein maaray jayen un ki nisbat yeh kehna ke woh marey hue hain ( woh murda nahi ) balkay zindah hain lekin tum nahi jantay
  2,155,aur hum kisi qader khauf aur bhook aur maal aur jaanun aur meoon ke nuqsaan se tumhari azmaish karen ge to sabar karne walon ko ( khuda ki khushnodi ki ) basharat suna do
  2,156,un logon par jab koi museebat waqay hoti hai to kehte hain ke hum khuda hi ka maal hain aur isi ki taraf lout kar jaane walay hain
  2,157,yahi log hain jin par un ke perwar-digaar ki meharbani aur rehmat hai. aur yahi seedhay raste par hain
  2,158,be shak ( koh ) Safa aur marwah khuda ki nishanyon mein se hain. to jo shakhs Khana kaaba ka hajj ya omra kere is par kuch gunah nahi ke dono ka tuwaf kere. ( balkay tuwaf aik qisam ka naik kaam hai ) aur jo koi naik kaam kere to khuda qader shanaas aur Dana hai
  2,159,jo log hamaray hukmon aur hdayton ko jo hum ne nazil ki hain ( kisi gharz fasid se ) chupatay hain bawajood yeh ke hum ne un logon ke ( samjhane ke ) liye apni kitaab mein khol khol kar bayan kardiya hai. aison par khuda aur tamam laanat karne walay laanat karte hain
  2,160,haan jo tauba karte hain aur apni haalat durust kar lete aur ( ehkaam Ellahi ko ) saaf saaf bayan kardete hain to mein un ke qasoor maaf kardaita hon aur mein bara maaf karne wala ( aur ) reham wala hon
  2,161,jo log kafir hue aur kafir hi marey aison par khuda ki aur firshton aur logon ki sab ki laanat
  2,162,woh hamesha isi ( laanat ) mein ( girftar ) rahen ge. un se nah to azaab hi halkakiya jaye ga aur nah inhen ( kuch ) mohlat miley gi
  2,163,aur ( logo ) tumhara mabood khuday-e wahid hai is barray meharban ( aur ) reham karne ke siwa koi ibadat ke Laiq nahi
  2,164,be shak asmano aur zameen ke peda karne mein aur raat aur din ke aik dosray ke peechay anay jaane mein aur kashtiyon aur jahazoo mein jo darya mein logon ke faiday ki cheeze le kar rawan hain aur meen mein jis ko khuda aasman se brsata aur is se zameen ko marnay ke baad zindah ( yani khushk hue peechay sirsabz ) kardaita hai aur zameen par har qisam ke janwar phelanay mein aur hawaon ke chalanay mein aur baadalon mein jo aasman aur zameen ke darmain ghiry rehtay hain. aqalmandon ke liye ( khuda ki qudrat ki ) nishanain hain
  2,165,aur baaz log aisay hain jo ghair khuda ko shareek ( khuda ) banatay aur un se khuda ki si mohabbat karte hain. lekin jo imaan walay hain woh to khuda hi ke sab se ziyada Dostdar hain. aur ae kash zalim log jo baat azaab ke waqt dekhen ge ab dekh letay ke sab terhan ki taaqat khuda hi ko hai. aur yeh ke khuda sakht azaab karne wala hai
  2,166,is din ( kufar ke ) peshwa apne pairon se bezari zahir karen ge aur ( dono ) azaab ( Ellahi ) dekh len ge aur un ke aapas ke taluqaat munhqita ho jaien ge
  2,167,( yeh haal dekh kar ) pairwi karne walay ( hasrat se ) kahin ge ke ae kash hamein phir duniya mein jana naseeb ho taakay jis terhan yeh hum se bezaar ho rahay hain isi terhan hum bhi un se bezaar hon. isi terhan khuda un ke aamaal inhen hasrat bana kar dukhaay gaavr woh dozakh se nikal nahi saken ge
  2,168,logo jo cheeze zameen mein halal Tayyab hain woh khao. aur shetan ke qadmon par nah chalo. woh tumhara khula dushman hai
  2,169,woh to tum ko buraiee aur be hiyai hi ke kaam karne ko kehta hai aur yeh bhi ke khuda ki nisbat aisi baatein kaho jin ka tumhe ( kuch bhi ) ilm nahi
  2,170,aur jab un logon se kaha jata hai ke jo ( kitaab ) khuda ne nazil farmai hai is ki pairwi karo to kehte hain ( nahi ) balkay hum to isi cheez ki pairwi karen ge jis par hum ne apne baap dada ko paaya. bhala agarchay un ke baap dada nah kuch samajte hon aur nah seedhay raste par hon ( tab bhi woh inhen ki taqleed kiye jayen ge )
  2,171,jo log kafir hain un ki misaal is shakhs ki si hai jo kisi aisi cheez ko aawaz day jo pukaar aur aawaz ke siwa kuch sun nah sakay. ( yeh ) behray hain gungay hain andhay hain ke ( kuch ) samajh hi nahi satke
  2,172,ae ahal imaan jo pakeeza cheeze hum ne tum ko ataa farmaen hain un ko khao aur agar khuda hi ke bande ho to is ( ki nematon ) ka shukar bhi ada karo
  2,173,is ne tum par mra howa janwar aur lahoo aur soor ka gosht aur jis cheez par khuda ke siwa kisi aur ka naam puraka jaye haraam kardiya hai haan jo nachar hojaye ( bashart e kay ) khuda ki nafarmani nah kere aur hadd ( zaroorat ) se bahar nah nikal jaye is par kuch gunah nahi. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala ( aur ) reham karne wala hai
  2,174,jo log ( khuda ) ki kitaab se un ( aayton aur hdayton ) ko jo is ne nazil farmai hain chupatay aur un ke badlay thori si qeemat ( yani dunyawi Manfiat ) haasil karte hain woh apne piton mein mehez aag bhartay hain. aisay logon se khuda qayamat ke din nah kalaam kere ga aur nah un ko ( gunaaho se ) pak kere ga. aur un ke liye dukh dainay wala azaab hai
  2,175,yeh woh log hain jinhon ne hadaayat chore kar gumraahi aur bakhshish chore kar azaab khareeda. yeh ( aatish ) jahannum ki kaisi bardasht karne walay hain !
  2,176,yeh is liye ke khuda ne kitaab sachaai ke sath nazil farmai. aur jin logon ne is kitaab mein ikhtilaafkiya woh zid mein ( aakar neki se ) daur ( hogaye ) hain
  2,177,neki yahi nahi ke tum mashriq ya maghrib ko ( qibla samajh kar un ) ki taraf munh karlo balkay neki yeh hai ke log khuda par aur roz akhirat par aur firshton par aur ( khuda ki ) kitaab par aur payghambaroon par imaan layein. aur maal bawajood Aziz rakhnay ke rishta daaron aur yatimon aur mohtajon aur musafiron aur mangnay walon ko den aur gardnon ( ke chhuranay ) mein ( kharch karen ) aur namaz parheen aur zakaat den. aur jab ehad karlen to is ko poora karen. aur sakhti aur takleef mein aur ( maarka ) kaarzar ke waqt saabit qadam rahen. yahi log hain jo ( imaan mein ) sachey hain aur yahi hain jo ( khuda se ) darny walay hain
  2,178,momino! tum ko mqtolon ke baray mein qisaas ( yani khoon ke badlay khoon ) ka hukum diya jata hai ( is terhan par ke ) azad ke badlay azad ( mara jaye ) aur ghulam ke badlay ghulam aur aurat ke badlay aurat aur qaatil ko is ke ( maqtool ) bhai ( ke qisaas mein ) se kuch maaf kardiya jaye to ( waris maqtool ) ko pasandeeda tareeq se ( qarar daad ki ) pairwi ( yani مطالبہٴ khoon baha ) karna aur ( qaatil ko ) khush khoi ke sath ada karna chahiye yeh perwar-digaar ki taraf se tumahray liye aasani aur meharbani hai jo is ke baad zayad-ti kere is ke liye dukh ka azaab hai
  2,179,aur ae ahal aqal ( hukum ) qisaas mein ( tumhari ) zindagani hai ke tum ( qatal o khonrizi se ) bachcho
  2,180,tum par farzkiya jata hai ke jab tum mein se kisi ko mout ka waqt aajay to agar woh kuch maal chore jaane wala ho to maa ba p aur rishta daaron ke liye dastoor ke mutabiq wasiyat krjaye ( khuda se ) dar ne walon par yeh aik haq hai
  2,181,jo shakhs wasiyat ko suneney ke baad badal daaley to is ( ke badalny ) ka gunah inhen logon par hai jo is ko badleen. aur be shak khuda santa jaanta hai
  2,182,agar kisi ko wasiyat karne walay ki taraf se ( kisi waris ki ) tarfdaari ya haq talfi ka andesha ho to agar woh ( wasiyat ko badal kar ) varson mein sulah krade to is par kuch gunah nahi. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala ( aur ) reham wala hai
  2,183,momino! tum par rozay farz kiye gay hain. jis terhan tum se pehlay logon par farz kiye gay they taakay tum parhaizgaar bano
  2,184,( rozon ke din ) ginti ke chand roz hain to jo shakhs tum mein se bemaar ho ya safar mein ho to dosray dinon mein rozon ka shumaar poora karle aur jo log roza rakhnay ki taaqat rakhen ( lekin rakhen nahi ) woh rozay ke badlay mohtaaj ko khana khula den aur jo koi shoq se neki kere to is ke haq mein ziyada acha hai. aur agar samjhoo to roza rakhna hi tumahray haq mein behtar hai
  2,185,( rozon ka maheena ) ramadaan ka maheena ( hai ) jis mein quran ( awwal awwal ) nazil howa jo logon ka rehnuma hai aur ( jis mein ) hadaayat ki khuli nishanain hain aur ( jo haq o baatil ko ) allag allag karne wala hai to jo koi tum mein se is mahinay mein mojood ho chahiye ke poooray mahinay ke rozay rakhay aur jo bemaar ho ya safar mein ho to dosray dinon mein ( rakh kar ) un ka shumaar poora karle. khuda tumahray haq mein aasani chahta hai aur sakhti nahi chahta aur ( yeh aasani ka hukum ) is liye ( diya gaya hai ) ke tum rozon ka shumaar poora karlo aur is ahsaan ke badlay ke khuda ne tum ko hadaayat bakhsh hai tum is ko buzurgi se yaad kar wa aur is ka shukar karo
  2,186,aur ( ae paighambar ) jab tum se mere bande mere baray mein daryaft karen to ( keh do ke ) mein to ( tumahray ) paas hon jab koi pukarnay wala mujhe pukaarta hai to mein is ki dua qubool karta hon to un ko chahiye ke mere hukmon ko manen aur mujh par imaan layein taakay naik rasta payen
  2,187,rozon ki raton mein tumahray liye apni aurton ke paas jana kardiya gaya hai woh tumhari poshak hain aur tum un ki poshak ho khuda ko maloom hai ke tum ( un ke paas jaane se ) apne haq mein khayanat karte they so is ne tum par meharbani ki aur tumhari harkaat se dar guzar farma. ab ( tum ko ikhtiyar hai ke ) un se mubashrat karo. aur khuda ne jo cheez tumahray liye likh rakhi hai ( yani aulaad ) is ko ( khuda se ) talab karo aur khao piyo yahan taq ke subah ki safaid dahari ( raat ki ) siyah dahari se allag nazar anay lagey. phir roza ( rakh kar ) raat taq poora karo aur jab tum masjidoon mein aitekaf baithy ho to un se mubashrat nah karo. yeh khuda ki hade hain un ke paas nah jana. isi terhan khuda apni ayatain logon ke ( samjhane ke ) liye khol khol kar bayan farmata hai taakay woh parhaizgaar banin
  2,188,aur aik dosray ka maal na-haq nah khao aur nah is ko ( rishwatan ) hakmon ke paas ponchao taakay logon ke maal ka kuch hissa najaaiz tor par kha jao aur ( usay ) tum jantay bhi ho
  2,189,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) log tum se naye chaand ke baray mein daryaft karte hain ( ke ghat-ta barhta kyun hai ) keh do ke woh logon ke ( kamon ki meaden ) aur hajj ke waqt maloom honay ka zareya hai aur neki is baat mein nahi ke ( ahram ki haalat mein ) gharon mein un ke pchhwarhe ki taraf se aao. balkay nekokaar woh hai jo parhaiz gaar ho aur gharon mein un ke darwazon se aaya karo aur khuda se drtay raho taakay nijaat pao
  2,190,aur jo log tum se lartay hain tum bhi khuda ki raah mein un se lrho magar zayad-ti nah karna ke khuda zayad-ti karne walon ko dost nahi rakhta
  2,191,aur un ko jahan pao qatal kardo aur jahan se unhon ne tum ko nikala hai ( yani mukkay se ) wahan se tum bhi un ko nikaal do. aur ( deen se gumraah karne ka ) fasaad qatal wa khoonzeri se kahin barh kar hai aur jab taq woh tum se masjid mohtaram ( yani khanah kaaba ) ke paas nah lrhin tum bhi wahan un se nah larna. haan agar woh tum se lrhin to tum un ko qatal kardalo. kafiroon ki yahi saza hai
  2,192,aur agar woh baz ajayeen to khuda bakhsnay wala ( aur ) reham karne wala hai
  2,193,aur un se is waqt taq lartay rehna ke fasaad nabood hojaye aur ( malik mein ) khuda hi ka deen hojaye aur agar woh ( fasaad se ) baz ajayeen to zaalmon ke siwa kisi par zayad-ti nahi ( karni chahiye )
  2,194,adab ka maheena adab ke mahinay ke maqabil hai aur adab ki cheeze aik dosray ka badla hain. pas agar koi tum par zayad-ti kere to jaisi zayad-ti woh tum par kere waisi hi tum is par karo. aur khuda se drtay raho aur jaan rakho ke khuda darny walon ke sath hai
  2,195,aur khuda ki raah mein ( maal ) kharch karo aur apne aap ko halakat mein nah daalo aur neki karo be shak khuda neki karne walon ko dost rakhta hai
  2,196,aur khuda ( ki khushnodi ) ke liye hajj aur omre ko poora karo. aur agar ( rastay mein ) rok liye jao to jaisi qurbani muyassar ho ( kardo ) aur jab taq qurbani apne maqam par nah poanch jaye sir nah mandao. aur agar koi tum mein bemaar ho ya is ke sir mein kisi terhan ki takleef ho to ( agar woh sir mandalay to ) is ke badlay rozay rakhay ya sadqa day ya qurbani kere phir jab ( takleef daur ho kar ) tum mutmaen hojao to jo ( tum mein ) hajj ke waqt taq omre se faida uthana chahay woh jaisi qurbani muyassar ho kere. aur jis ko ( qurbani ) nah miley woh teen rozay ayyaam hajj mein rakhay aur saat jab wapas ho. yeh poooray das hue. yeh hukum is shakhs ke liye hai jis ke ahal vayal mukkay mein nah rehtay hon aur khuda se drtay raho aur jaan rakho ke khuda sakht azaab dainay wala hai
  2,197,hajj ke mahinay ( Moueen hain jo ) maloom hain to shakhs un mahino mein hajj ki niyat karle to hajj ( ke dinon ) mein nah aurton se ikhtilaat kere nah koi bura kaam kere nah kisi se jhagrre. aur jo naik kaam tum karo ge woh khuda ko maloom hojaye ga aur zaad raah ( yani raste ka kharch ) sath le jao kyunkay behtar ( faida ) zaad raah ( ka ) parhaiz gari hai aur ae ahal aqal mujh se drtay raho
  2,198,is ka tumhe kuch gunah nahi ke ( hajj ke dinon mein ba zarea tijarat ) apne perwar-digaar se rozi talab karo aur jab Arfat se wapas honay lagu to Musher haraam ( yani mazdulfay ) mein khuda ka zikar karo aur is terhan zikar karo jis terhan is ne tum ko sikhaya. aur is se peshtar tum log ( un tareeqon se ) mehez nawaqif they
  2,199,phir jahan se aur log wapas hon wahein se tum bhi wapas ho aur khuda se bakhshish mango. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala aur rehmat karne wala hai
  2,200,phir jab hajj ke tamam arkaan poooray kar chuko to ( money mein ) khuda ko yaad karo. jis terhan apne baap dada ko yaadkiya karte they balkay is se bhi ziyada aur baaz log aisay hain jo ( khuda se ) iltija karte hain ke ae perwar-digaar hum ko ( jo duniya hai ) duniya hi mein inayat kar aisay logon ka akhirat mein kuch hissa nahi
  2,201,aur baze aisay hain ke dua karte hain ke perwar-digaar hum ko duniya mein bhi Nemat ataa farma aur akhirat mein bhi Nemat bakhshiyon aur dozakh ke azaab se mehfooz rakiyo
  2,202,yahi log hain jin ke liye un ke kamon ka hissa ( yani ajar naik tayyar ) hai aur khuda jald hisaab lainay wala ( aur jald ajar dainay wala ) hai
  2,203,aur ( qiyam money ke ) dinon mein ( jo ) ginti ke ( din mein ) khuda ko yaad karo. agar koi jaldi kere ( aur ) do hi din mein ( chal day ) to is par bhi kuch gunah nahi. aur jo baad taq thehra rahay is par bhi kuch gunah nahi. yeh baatein is shakhs ke liye hain jo ( khuda se ) daray aur tum log khuda se drtay raho aur jaan rakho ke tum sab is ke paas jama kiye jao ge .
  2,204,aur koi shakhs to aisa hai jis ki guftagu duniya ki zindagi mein tum ko dilkash maloom hoti hai aur woh apni maani alzhaimer par khuda ko gawah banata hai halaank woh sakht jhagralu hai
  2,205,aur jab peeth phair kar chala jata hai to zameen mein dorta phirta hai taakay is mein fitnah angazi kere aur khaiti ko ( barbaad ) aur ( insanon aur hewanon ki ) nasal ko nabood kardey aur khuda fitnah angazi ko pasand nahi karta
  2,206,aur jab is se kaha jata hai ke khuda se khauf kar to ghuroor is ko gunah mein phansa deta hai. so aisay ko jahannum sazawar hai. aur woh bohat bura thikana hai
  2,207,aur koi shakhs aisa hai ke khuda ki khushnodi haasil karne ke liye apni jaan beech dalta hai aur khuda bundon par bohat meharban hai
  2,208,momino! islam mein poooray poooray daakhil hojao aur shetan ke peechay nah chalo woh to tumhara Sarih dushman hai
  2,209,phir agar tum ehkaam roshan poanch jaane ke baad larkharajao to jaan jao ke khuda ghalib ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  2,210,kiya yeh log isi baat ke munhtazir hain ke un par khuda ( ka azaab ) baadal ke saybanon mein aa nazil ho aur farishtay bhi ( utar ayen ) aur kaam tamam kardiya jaye aur sab kamon ka rujoo khuda hi ki taraf hai
  2,211,( ae Mohammad ) bani Israel se pucho ke hum ne un ko kitni khuli nishanain den. aur jo shakhs khuda ki Nemat ko apne paas anay ke baad badal day to khuda sakht azaab karne wala hai
  2,212,aur jo kafir hain un ke liye duniya ki zindagi khushnuma kar di gayi hai aur woh mominoun se tamaskhur karte hain lekin jo parhaiz gaar hain woh qayamat ke din un par ghalib hon ge aur khuda jis ko chahta hai be shumaar rizaq deta hai
  2,213,( pehlay to sab ) logon ka aik hi mazhab tha ( lekin woh aapas mein ikhtilaaf karne lagey ) to khuda ne ( un ki taraf ) basharat dainay walay aur dar sunanay walay paighambar beje aur un par sachaai ke sath kitaaben nazil kee taakay jin umoor mein log ikhtilaaf karte they un ka un mein faisla kardey. aur is mein ikhtilaaf bhi inhen logon nekiya jin ko kitaab di gayi thi bawajood yeh ke un ke paas khulay hue ehkaam aachukay they ( aur yeh ikhtilaaf unhon ne sirf ) aapas ki zid se (kiya ) to jis amar haq mein woh ikhtilaaf karte they khuda ne apni meharbani se mominoun ko is ki raah dikha di. aur khuda jis ko chahta hai seedha rasta dikha deta hai
  2,214,kiya tum yeh khayaal karte ho ke ( yun hi ) bahisht mein daakhil hojao ge aur abhi tum ko pehlay logon ki si ( Mushkilain ) to paish aayi hi nahi. un ko ( barri barri ) skhtyan aur takleifein pohnchain aur woh ( savbton mein ) hila hila diye gay. yahan taq ke paighambar aur momin log jo un ke sath they sab pukaar utthay ke kab khuda ki madad aeye gi. dekho khuda ki madad ( an ) qareeb ( aaya chahti ) hai
  2,215,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) log tum se puchhte hain ke ( khuda ki raah mein ) kis terhan ka maal kharch karen. keh do ke ( jo chaho kharch karo lekin ) jo maal kharch karna chaho woh ( darja badarja ahal istehqaq yani ) maa baap aur qareeb ke rishte daaron ko aur yatimon ko aur mohtajon ko aur musafiron ko ( sab ko do ) aur jo bhalai tum karo ge khuda is ko jaanta hai
  2,217,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) log tum se izzat walay mahino mein larai karne ke baray mein daryaft karte hain keh do ke un mein larna bara ( gunah ) hai aur khuda ki raah se rokna aur is se kufar karna aur masjid haraam ( yani khanah kaaba mein jaane ) se ( band karna ). aur ahal masjid ko is mein se nikaal dena ( jo yeh kufar karte hain ) khuda ke nazdeek is se bhi ziyada ( gunah ) hai. aur fitnah angazi khonrizi se bhi barh kar hai. aur yeh log hamesha tum se lartay rahen ge yahan taq ke agar Maqdoor rakhen to tum ko tumahray deen se phair den. aur jo koi tum mein se apne deen se phir kar ( kafir ho ) jaye ga aur kafir hi marey ga to aisay logon ke aamaal duniya aur akhirat dono mein barbaad ho jaien ge aur yahi log dozakh ( mein jaane ) walay hain jis mein hamesha rahen ge
  2,218,jo log imaan laaye aur khuda ke liye watan chore gay aur ( kufar se ) jung karte rahay wohi khuda ki rehmat ke umeed waar hain. aur khuda bakhsnay wala ( aur ) rehmat karne wala hai
  2,219,( ae paighambar ) log tum se sharaab aur juye ka hukum daryaft karte hain. keh do ke un mein nuqsaan barray hain aur logon ke liye kuch faiday bhi hain magar un ke nuqsaan faido se kahin ziyada hain aur yeh bhi tum se puchhte hain ke ( khuda ki raah mein ) kon sa maal kharch karen. keh do ke jo zaroorat se ziyada ho. is terhan khuda tumahray liye apne ehkaam khol khol kar bayan farmata hai taakay tum socho
  2,220,( yani ) duniya aur akhirat ( ki baton ) mein ( ghhor karo ). aur tum se yatimon ke baray mein daryaft karte hain keh do ke un ki ( haalat ki ) islaah bohat acha kaam hai. aur agar tum un se mil jal kar rehna ( yani kharch akatha rakhna ) chaho to woh tumahray bhai hain aur khuda khoob jaanta hai ke kharabi karne wala kon hai aur islaah karne wala kon. aur agar khuda chahta to tum ko takleef mein daal deta. be shak khuda ghalib ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  2,221,aur ( momino ) mushriq aurton se jab taq ke imaan nah layein nikah nah karna. kyunkay mushriq aurat khuwa tum ko kaisi hi bhali lagey is se momin londi behtar hai. aur ( isi terhan ) mushriq mard jab taq imaan nah layein momin aurton ko un ko zojiat mein nah dena kyunkay mushriq ( mard ) se khuwa woh tum ko kaisa hi bhala lagey momin ghulam behtar hai. yeh ( mushriq logon ko ) dozakh ki taraf bulatay hain. aur khuda apni meharbani se bahisht aur bakhshish ki taraf bulaataa hai. aur apne hukum logon se khol khol kar bayan karta hai taakay nasiyaat haasil karen
  2,222,aur tum se haiz ke baray mein daryaft karte hain. keh do ke woh to najasat hai. so ayyaam haiz mein aurton se kinara kash raho. aur jab taq pak nah ho jaien un se maqarbat nah karo. haan jab pak ho jaien to jis tareeq se khuda ne irshad farmaya hai un ke paas jao. kuch shak nahi ke khuda tauba karne walon aur pak saaf rehne walon ko dost rakhta hai
  2,223,tumhari aurtain tumharai khaiti hain to apni khaiti mein jis terhan chaho jao. aur apne liye ( naik amal ) agay bhaijho. aur khuda se drtay raho aur jaan rakho ke ( aik din ) tumhe is ke rubaroo haazir hona hai aur ( ae paighambar ) imaan walon ko basharat suna do
  2,224,aur khuda ( ke naam ko ) is baat ka heela nah banana ke ( is ki ) kasmain kha kha kar sulooq karne aur parhaiz gari karne aur logon mein sulah osazgari karanay se ruk jao. aur khuda sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai
  2,225,khuda tumhari laghu qasmon par tum se muwakhza nah kere ga. lekin jo kasmain tum qasad dili se khao ge un par muwakhza kere ga. aur khuda bakhsnay wala Burdbar hai
  2,226,jo log apni aurton ke paas jaane se qasam khalin un ko chaar mahinay taq intzaar karna chahiye. agar ( is arsay mein qasam se ) rujoo karlen to khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  2,227,aur agar Talaq ka iradah karlen to bhi khuda santa ( aur ) jaanta hai
  2,228,aur Talaq wali aurtain teen haiz taq apni tain rokay rahen. aur agar woh khuda aur roz qayamat par imaan rakhti hain to un ka jaaiz nahi ke khuda ne jo kuch un ke shikam mein pedakiya hai is ko chupayen. aur un ke khawand agar phir muwafiqat chahain to is ( muddat ) mein woh un ko apni zojiat mein le lainay ke ziyada haqdaar hain. aur aurton ka haq ( mardon par ) waisa hi hai jaisay dastoor ke mutabiq ( mardon ka haq ) aurton par hai. Albata mardon ko aurton par fazeelat hai. aur khuda ghalib ( aur ) sahib hikmat hai
  2,229,Talaq ( sirf ) dobaar hai ( yani jab do dafaa Talaq day di jaye to ) phir ( aurton ko ) ya to ba-tareeq shaista ( nikah mein ) rehne dena ya bhalai ke sath chore dena. aur yeh jaaiz nahi ke jo mohar tum un ko day chuke ho is mein se kuch wapas le lau. haan agar zan o shohar ko khauf ho ke woh khuda ki hado ko qaim nahi rakh saken ge to agar aurat ( khawand ke haath se ) rihayi panay ke badlay mein kuch day daaley to dono par kuch gunah nahi. yeh khuda ki ( muqarrar ki hui ) hade hain un se bahar nah niklana. aur jo log khuda ki hado se bahar nikal jayen ge woh gunehgaar hon ge
  2,230,phir agar shohar ( do tlaqon ke baad teesri ) Talaq aurat ko day day to is ke baad jab taq aurat kisi dosray shakhs se nikah nah karle is ( pehlay shohar ) par halal nah hogi. haan agar dosra khawand bhi Talaq day day aur aurat aur pehla khawand phir aik dosray ki taraf rujoo karlen to un par kuch gunah nahi bashart e kay dono yaqeen karen ke khuda ki hado ko qaim rakh saken ge aur yeh khuda ki hade hain un ko woh un logon ke liye bayan farmata hai jo Danish rakhtay hain
  2,231,aur jab tum aurton ko ( do dafaa ) Talaq day chicco aur un ki adt poori hojaye to inhen ya to husn sulooq se nikah mein rehne do ya ba-tareeq shaista rukhsat kardo aur is niyat se un ko nikah mein nah rehne dena chahiye ke inhen takleef do aur un par zayad-ti karo. aur jo aisa kere ga woh apna hi nuqsaan kere ga aur khuda ke ehkaam ko hansi ( aur khail ) nah banaao aur khuda ne tum ko jo naematain bakhsh hain aur tum par jo kitaab aur danai ki baatein nazil ki hain jin se woh tumhe nasiyaat farmata hai un ko yaad karo. aur khuda se drtay raho aur jaan rakho keh khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
  2,232,aur jab tum aurton ko Talaq day chicco aur un ki adt poori hojaye to un ko dosray shohron ke sath jab woh aapas mein jaaiz tor par raazi ho jaien nikah karne se mat roko. is ( hukum ) se is shakhs ko nasiyaat ki jati hai jo tum mein khuda aur roz akhirat par yaqeen rakhta hai. yeh tumahray liye nihayat khoob aur bohat pakizgee ki baat hai aur khuda jaanta hai aur tum nahi jantay
  2,233,aur maaen apne bachon ko poooray do saal doodh pilain yeh ( hukum ) is shakhs ke liye hai jo poori muddat taq doodh pilwana chahay. aur doodh pilanay wali maaon ka khana aur kapra dastoor ke mutabiq baap ke zimmay hoga. kisi shakhs ko is ki taaqat se ziyada takleef nahi di jati ( to yaad rakho ke ) nah to maa ko is ke bachay ke sabab nuqsaan pohanchaya jaye aur nah baap ko is ki aulaad ki wajah se nuqsaan pohanchaya jaye aur isi terhan ( nan nfqh ) bachay ke waris ke zimmay hai. aur agar dono ( yani maa baap ) aapas ki razamandi aur Salah se bachay ka doodh chhurana chahain to un par kuch gunah nahi. aur agar tum apni aulaad ko doodh pilwana chaho to tum par kuch gunah nahi bashart e kay tum doodh pilanay valyon ko dastoor ke mutabiq un ka haq jo tum ne denakiya tha day do aur khuda se drtay raho aur jaan rakho ke jo kuch tum karte ho khuda is ko dekh raha hai
  2,234,aur jo log tum mein se mrjayin aur aurtain chore jayen to aurtain chaar mahinay das din apne aap ko rokay rahen. aur jab ( yeh ) adt poori krchkin aur apne haq mein pasandeeda kaam ( yani nikah ) karlen to un par kuch gunah nahi. aur khuda tumahray sab kamon se waaqif hai
  2,235,aur agar tum knaye ki baton mein aurton ko nikah ka pegham bhaijho ya ( nikah ki khwahish ko ) apne dilon mein makhfi rakho to to tum par kuch gunah nahi. khuda ko maloom hai ke tum un se ( nikah ka ) zikar karo ge. magar ( ayyaam adt mein ) is ke siwa ke dastoor ke mutabiq koi baat keh do posheeda tor par un se qoul wa iqraar nah karna. aur jab taq adt poori nah haulay nikah ka pukhta iradah nah karna. aur jaan rakho ke jo kuch tumahray dilon mein hai khuda ko sab maloom hai to is se drtay raho aur jaan rakho ke khuda bakhsnay wala aur halm wala hai
  2,236,aur agar tum aurton ko un ke paas jaane ya un ka mohar muqarrar karne se pehlay Talaq day do to tum par kuch gunah nahi. haan un ko dastoor ke mutabiq kuch kharch zaroor do ( yani ) Maqdoor wala apne Maqdoor ke mutabiq day aur tangdast apni hesiyat ke mutabiq. naik logon par yeh aik terhan ka haq hai
  2,237,aur agar tum aurton ko un ke paas jaane se pehlay Talaq day do lekin mohar muqarrar kar chukay ho to aadha mohar dena hoga. haan agar aurtain mohar bakhash den ya mard jin ke haath mein Aqab nikah hai ( apna haq ) chore den. ( aur poora mohar day den to un ko ikhtiyar hai ) aur agar tum mard log hay apna haq chore do to yeh parhaiz gari ki baat hai. aur aapas mein bhalai karne ko faramosh nah karna. kuch shak nahi ke khuda tumahray sab kamon ko dekh raha hai
  2,238,( mslmano ) sab namazain khasosan beech ki namaz ( yani namaz asar ) poooray iltazam ke sath ada karte raho. aur khuda ke agay adab se kharray raha karo
  2,239,agar tum khauf ki haalat mein ho to payaday ya sawaar ( jis haal mein ho namaz parh lau ) phir jab aman ( wa itmenaan ) hojaye to jis tareeq se khuda ne tum ko sikhaya hai jo tum pehlay nahi jantay they khuda ko yaad karo
  2,240,aur jo log tum mein se mrjayin aur aurtain chore jayen woh apni aurton ke haq mein wasiyat krjayin ke un ko aik saal taq kharch diya jaye aur ghar se nah nikaali jayen. haan agar woh khud ghar se nikal jayen aur apne haq mein pasandeeda kaam ( yani nikah ) karlen to tum par kuch gunah nahi. aur khuda zabardast hikmat wala hai
  2,241,aur mutalqa aurton ko bhi dastoor ke mutabiq nan o nfqh dena chahiye parhaiz garon par ( yeh bhi ) haq hai
  2,242,isi terhan khuda apne ehkaam tumahray liye bayan farmata hai taakay tum samjhoo
  2,243,bhala tum ne un logon ko nahi dekha jo ( shumaar mein ) hazaron hi they aur mout ke dar se apne gharon se nikal bhage they. to khuda ne un ko hukum diya ke marjao. phir un ko zindah bhi kardiya. kuch shak nahi ke khuda logon par meharbani rakhta hai. lekin aksar log shukar nahi karte
  2,244,aur ( mslmano ) khuda ki raah mein jehaad karo aur jaan rakho ke khuda ( sab kuch ) jaanta hai
  2,245,koi hai ke khuda ko qarz husna day ke woh is ke badlay is ko kayi hissay ziyada day ga. aur khuda hi rozi ko tang karta aur ( wohi usay ) kushadah karta hai. aur tum isi ki taraf lout kar jao ge
  2,246,bhala tum ne bani Israel ki aik jamaat ko nahi dekha jis ne moose ke baad apne paighambar se kaha ke aap hamaray liye aik badshah muqarrar kar dein taakay hum khuda ki raah mein jehaad karen. paighambar ne kaha ke agar tum ko jehaad ka hukum diya jaye to ajab nahi ke larnay se pehlu tehi karo. woh kehnay lagey ke hum raah khuda mein kyun nah lrhin ge jab ke hum watan se ( kharij ) aur baal bachon se judda kardiye gay. lekin jab un ko jehaad ka hukum diya gaya to chand ashkhaas ke siwa sab phir gay. aur khuda zaalmon se khoob waaqif hai
  2,247,aur paighambar ne un se ( yeh bhi ) kaha ke khuda ne tum par Taloot ko badshah muqarrar farmaya hai. woh bolay ke usay hum par badshahi ka haq kyonkr ho sakta hai badshahi ke mustahiq to hum hain aur is ke paas to bohat si doulat bhi nahi. paighambar ne kaha ke khuda ne is ko tum par fazeelat di hai aur ( badshahi ke liye ) munhtakhib farmaya hai is ne usay ilm bhi bohat sa bakhsha hai aur tan o توش bhi ( bara ataakiya hai ) aur khuda ( ko ikhtiyar hai ) jisay chahay badshahi bakhshay. woh bara kashaish wala aur Dana hai
  2,248,aur paighambar ne un se kaha ke un ki badshahi ki nishani yeh hai ke tumahray paas aik sandooq aeye ga jis ko farishtay uthaye hue hon ge is mein tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tasalii ( bakhsnay wali cheez ) hogi aur kuch aur cheeze bhi hon gi jo moose aur Haroon chore gay they. agar tum imaan rakhtay ho to yeh tumahray liye aik barri nishani hai
  2,249,gharz jab Taloot faujein le kar rawana howa to is ne ( un se ) kaha ke khuda aik neher se tumhari azmaish karne wala hai. jo shakhs is mein se pani pi le ga ( is ki nisbat tasawwurkiya jaye ga ke ) woh mera nahi. aur jo nah piye ga woh ( samgha jaye ga ke ) mera hai. haan agar koi haath se chalo bhar pani pi le ( to kher. jab woh log neher par puhanche ) to chand shakhson ke siwa sab ne pani pi liya. phir jab Taloot aur momin log jo is ke sath they neher ke paar hogaye. to kehnay lagey ke aaj hum mein Jalut aur is ke lashkar se muqaabla karne ki taaqat nahi. jo log yaqeen rakhtay they ke un ko khuda ke rubaroo haazir hona hai woh kehnay lagey ke bsaavqat thori si jamaat ne khuda ke hukum se barri jamaat par fatah haasil ki hai aur khuda istiqlal rakhnay walon ke sath hai
  2,250,aur jab woh log Jalut aur is ke lashkar ke maqabil aeye to ( khuda se ) dua ki ke ae perwar-digaar hum par sabr ke dhanay khol day aur hamein ( larai mein ) saabit qadam rakh aur ( lashkar ) kufar par fatahyaab kar
  2,251,to Taloot ki fouj ne khuda ke hukum se un ko hazeemat di. aur dawod ne Jalut ko qatal kar dala. aur khuda ne is ko badshahi aur danai bakhsh aur jo kuch chaha sikhaya. aur khuda logon ko aik dosray ( par charhai aur hamla karne ) se htata nah rehta to malik tabah hojata lekin khuda ahal aalam par bara meharban hai
  2,252,yeh khuda ki ayatain hain jo hum tum ko sachaai ke sath parh kar sunaate hain ( aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tum bilashuba payghambaroon mein se ho
  2,253,yeh paighambar ( jo hum vqtan foqtan bhaijtay rahen hain ) un mein se hum ne baaz ko baaz par fazeelat di hai. baaz aisay hain jin se khuda ne guftagu farmai aur baaz ke ( dosray umoor mein ) martabay buland kiye. aur eesa ban maryam ko hum ne khuli hui nishanain ataa kee aur rooh al quds se un ko madad di. aur agar khuda chahta to un se pichlle log apne paas khuli nishanain anay ke baad aapas mein nah lartay lekin unhon ne ikhtilaafkiya to un mein se baaz to imaan le aeye aur baaz kafir hi rahay. aur agar khuda chahta to yeh log baahum jung o qtal nah karte. lekin khuda jo chahta hai karta hai
  2,254,ae imaan walo jo ( maal ) hum ne tum ko diya hai is mein se is din ke anay se pehlay pehlay kharch karlo jis mein nah ( aamaal ka ) soda ho aur nah dosti aur sifarish ho sakay aur kufar karne walay log zalim hain
  2,255,khuda ( woh mabood brhq hai ke ) is ke siwa koi ibadat ke Laiq nahi zindah hamesha rehne wala usay nah ongh aati hai nah neend jo kuch asmano mein aur jo kuch zameen mein hain sab isi ka hai kon hai jo is ki ijazat ke baghair is se ( kisi ki ) sifarish kar sakay jo kuch logon ke rubaroo ho raha hai aur jo kuch un ke peechay hochuka hai usay sab maloom hai aur woh is ki maloomat mein se kisi cheez par dustarus haasil nahi kar satke haan jis qader woh chahta hai ( isi qader maloom kara deta hai ) is ki badshahi ( aur ilm ) aasman aur zameen sab par haawi hai aur usay un ki hifazat kuch bhi dushwaar nahi woh bara aliiiii rutba aur jallel al-qadar hai
  2,256,deen ( islam ) mein zabardasti nahi hai hadaayat ( saaf tor par zahir aur ) gumraahi se allag ho chuki hai to jo shakhs buton se aitqaad nah rakhay aur khuda par imaan laaye is ne aisi mazboot rassi haath mein pakar li hai jo kabhi totnay wali nahi aur khuda ( sab kuch ) santa aur ( sab kuch ) jaanta hai
  2,257,jo log imaan laaye hain un ka dost khuda hai ke unn ko andheray se nikaal kar roshni mein le jata hai aur jo kafir hain un ke dost shetan hain ke un ko roshni se nikaal kar andheray mein le jatay hain yahi log ahal dozakh hain ke is mein hamesha rahen ge
  2,258,bhala tum ne is shakhs ko nahi dekha jo is ( ghuroor ke ) sabab se ke khuda ne is ko saltanat bakhsh thi ibrahim se perwar-digaar ke baray mein jhagrnay laga. jab ibrahim ne kaha mera perwar-digaar to woh hai jo jalataa aur maarta hai. woh bola ke jala aur maar to mein bhi sakta hon. ibrahim ne kaha ke khuda to Sooraj ko mashriq se nkalta hai aap usay maghrib se nikaal dijiye ( yeh sun kar ) kafir heran reh gaya aur khuda be insafon ko hadaayat nahi diya karta
  2,259,ya isi terhan is shakhs ko ( nahi dekha ) jisay aik gaon mein jo apni chaton par gira para tha ittafaq guzar howa. to is ne kaha ke khuda is ( ke bashindon ) ko marnay ke baad kyonkr zindah kere ga. to khuda ne is ki rooh qabz karli ( aur ) so baras taq ( is ko murda rakha ) phir is ko jala uthaya aur poocha tum kitna arsa ( marey ) rahay ho is ne jawab diya ke aik din ya is se bhi kam. khuda ne farmaya ( nahi ) balkay so baras ( marey ) rahay ho. aur apne khanay peenay ki cheezon ko dekho ke ( itni muddat mein mutlaq ) sari basi nahi aur apne gadhay ko bhi dekho ( jo mra para hai ) gharz ( un baton se ) yeh hai ke hum tum ko logon ke liye ( apni qudrat ki ) nishani banayen aur ( haan gadhay ) ki hadion ko dekho ke hum un ko kyonkr jore dete aur un par ( kis terhan ) gosht post charha dete hain. jab yeh waqeat is ke mushahiday mein aeye to bol utha ke mein yaqeen karta hon ke khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
  2,260,aur jab ibrahim ne ( khuda se ) kaha ke ae perwar-digaar mujhe dikha ke to mardon ko kyonkr zindah kere ga. khuda ne farmayakiya tum ne ( is baat ko ) bawar nahikiya. unhon ne kaha kyun nahi. lekin ( mein dekhna ) is liye ( chahta hon ) ke mera dil itminan kaamil haasil karle. khuda ne farmaya ke chaar janwar pakarwa kar apne paas mannga lau ( aur tukre tukre karado ) phir un ka aik tukda har aik pahar par rkhwa do phir un ko bulaao to woh tumahray paas dorrtay chalay ayen ge. aur jaan rakho ke khuda ghalib aur sahib hikmat hai .
  2,261,jo log apna maal khuda ki raah mein kharch karte hain un ( ke maal ) ki misaal is danay ki si hai jis se saat balen ugen aur har aik baal mein so so danay hon aur khuda jis ( ke maal ) ko chahta hai ziyada karta hai. woh barri kashaish wala aur sab kuch jan-nay wala hai
  2,262,jo log apna maal khuda ke raste mein sirf karte hain phir is ke baad nah is kharch ka ( kisi par ) ahsaan rakhtay hain aur nah ( kisi ko ) takleef dete hain. un ka sila un ke perwar-digaar ke paas ( tayyar ) hai. aur ( qayamat ke roz ) nah un ko kuch khauf hoga aur nah woh ghamgeen hon ge
  2,263,jis khairaat dainay ke baad ( lainay walay ko ) aeza di jaye is se to naram baat keh dainee aur ( is ki be adbi se ) dar guzar karna behtar hai aur khuda be parwa aur Burdbar hai
  2,264,momino! apne sadqat ( wa kherat ) ahsaan rakhnay aur aeza dainay se is shakhs ki terhan barbaad nah kar dena. jo logon ko dikhavay ke liye maal kharch karta hai aur khuda aur roz akhirat par imaan nahi rakhta. to is ( ke maal ) ki misaal is chattaan ki si hai jis par thori si matti pari ho aur is par zor ka meen baras kar usay saaf kar daaley. ( isi terhan ) yeh ( riakaar ) log apne aamaal ka kuch bhi sila haasil nahi kar saken ge. aur khuda aisay nashukron ko hadaayat nahi diya karta
  2,265,aur jo log khuda ki khushnodi haasil karne ke liye khuloos niyat se apna maal kharch karte hain un ki misaal aik baagh ki si hai jo onche jagah par waqay ho ( jab ) is par meen parre to dugna phal laaye. aur agar meen nah bhi parre to kher phwaar hi sahi aur khuda tumahray kamon ko dekh raha hai
  2,266,bhala tum mein koi yeh chahta hai ke is ka khajoron aur angarro ka baagh ho jis mein nehrain beh rahi hon aur is mein is ke liye har qisam ke meway mojood hon aur usay burhapa a pakray aur is ke nanhay nanhay bachay bhi hon. to ( nagahan ) is baagh par aag ka bhara howa bagola chalay aur woh jal kar ( raakh ka dhair ho ) jaye. is terhan khuda tum se apni ayatain khol khol kar bayan farmata hai taakay tum socho ( aur samjhoo )
  2,267,momino! jo pakeeza aur umdah maal tum kamate hon aur jo cheeze hum tumahray liye zameen se nikaltay hain un mein se ( raah khuda mein ) kharch karo. aur buri aur napak cheeze dainay ka qasad nah karna ke ( agar woh cheeze tumhe di jayen to ) bajuz is ke ke ( letay waqt ) ankhen band karlo un ko kabhi nah lau. aur jaan rakho ke khuda be parwa ( aur ) qabil sataish hai
  2,268,( aur dekhna ) shetan ( ka kehna nah maanna woh ) tumhe tang dasti ka khauf dilaata aur be hiyai ke kaam kar ne ko kehta hai. aur khuda tum se apni bakhshish aur rehmat ka wada karta hai. aur khuda barri kashaish wala ( aur ) sab kuch jan-nay wala hai
  2,269,woh jis ko chahta hai danai bkhshta hai. aur jis ko danai mili be shak is ko barri Nemat mili. aur nasiyaat to wohi log qubool karte hain jo aqalmand hain
  2,270,aur tum ( khuda ki raah mein ) jis terhan ka kharch karo ya koi Nazar manu khuda is ko jaanta hai aur zaalmon ka koi madadgaar nahi
  2,271,agar tum khairaat zahir do to woh bhi khoob hai aur agar posheeda do aur do bhi ahal haajat ko to woh khoob tar hai aur ( is terhan ka dena ) tumahray gunaaho ko bhi daur kardey ga. aur khuda ko tumahray sab kamon ki khabar hai
  2,272,"( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tum un logon ki hadaayat ke zimma daar nahi ho balkay khuda hi jis ko chahta hai hadaayat bkhshta hai. aur ( momino ) tum jo maal kharch karo ge to is ka faida tumhe ko hai aur tum jo kharch karo ge khuda ki khushnodi ke liye karo ge. aur jo maal tum kharch karo ge woh tumhe poora poora day diya jaye ga aur tumhara kuch nuqsaan nahikiya jaye ga ,"
  2,273,( aur haan tum jo kharch karo ge to ) un hajatmandon ke liye jo khuda ki raah mein ruke baithy hain aur malik mein kisi taraf jaane ki taaqat nahi rakhtay ( aur mangnay se aar rakhtay hain ) yahan taq ke nah mangnay ki wajah se nawaqif shakhs un ko ghanni khayaal karta hai aur tum qayafay se un ko saaf pehchan lau ( ke hajatmand hain aur sharam ke sabab ) logon se ( munh phore kar aur ) lapat kar nahi maang satke aur tum jo maal kharch karo ge kuch shak nahi ke khuda is ko jaanta hai
  2,274,jo log apna maal raat aur din aur posheeda aur zahir ( raah khuda mein ) kharch karte rehtay hain un ka sila perwar-digaar ke paas hai aur un ko ( qayamat ke din ) nah kisi terhan ka khauf hoga aur nah gham
  2,275,jo log sood khatay hain woh ( qabron se ) is terhan ( hawaas bakhta ) utheen ge jaisay kisi ko jin ne lapat kar deewana bana diya ho yeh is liye ke woh kehte hain ke soda bechna bhi to ( naffa ke lehaaz se ) waisa hi hai jaisay sood ( lena ) halaank saudey ko khuda ne halalkiya hai aur sood ko haraam. to jis shakhs ke paas khuda ki nasiyaat pohanchi aur woh ( sood lainay se ) baz agaya to jo pehlay hochuka woh is ka. aur ( qayamat mein ) is ka maamla khuda ke supurd aur jo phir lainay laga to aisay log dozakhi hain ke hamesha dozakh mein ( jaltay ) rahen ge
  2,276,khuda sood ko nabood ( yani be barket ) karta aur khairaat ( ki barket ) ko berhata hai aur khuda kisi nashukray gunehgaar ko dost nahi rakhta
  2,277,jo log imaan laaye aur naik amal karte aur namaz parhte aur zakaat dete rahay un ko un ke kamon ka sila khuda ke haan miley ga aur ( qayamat ke din ) un ko nah kuch khauf howa aur nah woh ghumnaak hon ge
  2,278,momino! khuda se daro aur agar imaan rakhtay ho to jitna sood baqi reh gaya hai is ko chore do
  2,279,agar aisa nah karo ge to khabardaar hojao ( ke tum ) khuda aur rasool se jung karne ke liye ( tayyar hotay ho ) aur agar tauba karlo ge ( aur sood chore do ge ) to tum ko apni asal raqam lainay ka haq hai jis mein nah ouron ka nuqsaan aur tumhara nuqsaan
  2,280,aur agar qarz lainay wala tang dast ho to ( usay ) kashaish ( ke haasil honay ) taq mohlat ( do ) aur agar ( zar qarz ) bakhash hi do to tumharay liye ziyada acha hai bashart e kay samjhoo
  2,281,aur is din se daro jab ke tum khuda ke huzoor mein lout kar jao ge aur har shakhs apne aamaal ka poora poora badla paye ga. aur kisi ka kuch nuqsaan nah hoga
  2,282,momino! jab tum aapas mein kisi meyaad Moueen ke liye qarz ka maamla karne lagu to is ko likh liya karo aur likhnay wala tum mein ( kisi ka nuqsaan nah kere balkay ) insaaf se likhay neez likhnay wala jaissa usay khuda ne sikhaya hai likhnay se inkaar bhi nah kere aur dastaweez likh day. aur jo shakhs qarz le wohi ( dastaweez ka ) mazmoon bol kar likhwaye aur khuda se ke is ka maalik hai khauf kere aur zar qarz mein se kuch kam nah likhwaye. aur agar qarz lainay wala be aqal ya zaeef ho ya mazmoon lkhwane ki qabliyat nah rakhta ho to jo is ka walii ho woh insaaf ke sath mazmoon likhwaye. aur apne mein se do mardon ko ( aisay muamlay ke ) gawah karliya karo. aur agar do mard nah hon to aik mard aur do aurtain jin ko tum gawah pasand karo ( kaafi hain ) ke agar un mein se aik bhool jaye gi to doosri usay yaad dlade gi. aur jab gawah ( gawahi ke liye talab kiye jayen to inkaar nah karen. aur qarz thora ho ya bohat is ( ki dastaweez ) ke likhnay mein kahili nah karna. yeh baat khuda ke nazdeek nihayat qareen insaaf hai aur shahadat ke liye bhi yeh bohat durust tareeqa hai. is se tumhe kisi terhan ka shak woh shuba bhi nahi parre ga. haan agar soda dast bdst ho jo tum aapas mein letay dete ho to agar ( aisay muamlay ki ) dastaweez nah likho to tum par kuch gunah nahi. aur jab khareed vfrokhtkiya karo to bhi gawah karliya karo. aur katib dastaweez aur gawah ( maamla karne walon ka ) kisi terhan nuqsaan nah karen. agar tum ( log ) aisa karo to yeh tumahray liye gunah ki baat hai. aur khuda se daro aur ( dekho ke ) woh tum ko ( kaisi mufeed baatein ) sakata hai aur khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
  2,283,aur agar tum safar par hwavr ( dastaweez ) likhnay wala mil nah sakay to ( koi cheez ) rehan ya qabza rakh kar ( qarz le lau ) aur agar koi kisi ko amin samjhay ( yani rehan ke baghair qarz deeday ) to amanatdar ko chahiye ke sahib amanat ki amanat ada kardey aur khuda se jo is ka perwar-digaar hai daray. aur ( dekhna ) shahadat ko mat chhupana. jo is ko chupaye ga woh dil ka gunehgaar hoga. aur khuda tumahray sab kamon se waaqif hai
  2,284,jo kuch asmano mein aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab khuda hi ka hai. tum apne dilon ki baat ko zahir karo ge to ya chupao ge to khuda tum se is ka hisaab le ga phir woh jisay chahay mughfirat kere aur jisay chahay azaab day. aur khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
  2,285,rasool ( khuda ) is kitaab par jo un ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se un par nazil hui imaan rakhtay hain aur momin bhi. sab khuda par aur is ke firshton par aur is ki kitabon par aur is ke payghambaroon par imaan rakhtay hain ( aur kehtay hain ke ) hum is ke payghambaroon se kisi mein kuch farq nahi karte aur woh ( khuda se ) arz karte hain ke hum ne ( tera hukum ) suna aur quboolkiya. ae perwar-digaar hum teri bakhshish mangte hain aur teri hi taraf lout kar jana hai
  2,286,khuda kisi shakhs ko is ki taaqat se ziyada takleef nahi deta. achay kaam kere ga to is ko un ka faida miley ga buray kere ga to usay un ka nuqsaan puhanche ga. ae perwar-digaar agar hum se bhool ya chowk hogayi ho to hum se moakhza nah kejio. ae perwar-digaar hum par aisa boojh nah daliyon jaissa to ne hum se pehlay logon par dala tha. ae perwar-digaar jitna boojh uthany ki hum mein taaqat nahi itna hamaray sir par nah rakiyo. aur ( ae perwar-digaar ) hamaray gunaaho se dar guzar kar aur hamein bakhash day. aur hum par reham farma. to hi hamara maalik hai aur hum ko kafiroon par ghalib farma
